  <md:abstract><para>By the end of this section, you will be able to:</para><list>
<item>Define gauge pressure and absolute pressure</item>
<item>Explain various methods for measuring pressure</item>
<item>Understand the working of open-tube barometers</item>
<item>Describe in detail how manometers and barometers operate</item>
</list></md:abstract>
